<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Victhon</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #000;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            color: #fff;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        .content h2 {
            color: #1a1a1a;
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        .content p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f1f1f1;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background-color: #000;
            color: #fff !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Victhon</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Welcome to the community, <%= name %>!</h2>
            <p>We are thrilled to have you on board. Victhon is dedicated to connecting you with the best service providers across the country, making every job easier and every connection more professional.</p>
            <p>Our platform ensures secure payments, verified professionals, and real-time tracking for your peace of mind.</p>
            <p>Get started today by exploring our wide range of services or completing your profile to start receiving job requests.</p>
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="https://victhon.co" class="btn">Explore Services</a>
            </div>
            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">Best regards,<br>The Victhon Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            &copy; 2026 Victhon Platform. All rights reserved.<br>
            Connecting you to the best service providers.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
